        @Nullable
public static Plugin instance()
        Obtains the instance of the plugin which the caller class is in

        Returns null if the plugin has not been loaded yet, or if the class is not a plugin loaded on the server.

        Returns:
        the instance of the plugin

      • instance

public static <T extends Plugin> T instance(Class<T> c)
